|---|---|---|
| No security headers (Helmet) | 🔴 High | Low |
| No global error handler / stack leak | 🔴 High | Low |
| No rate limiting | 🟠 Medium | Low |
| No input validation framework | 🟠 Medium | Low |
| No CORS configuration | 🟠 Medium | Low |
| No body parser with size limits | 🟡 Low | Low |
| Hardcoded port | 🟡 Low | Low |
